'''Lagabee''' was the [[Capital/Legends|capital]] [[City/Legends|city]] of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Ord Tiddell/Legends|Ord Tiddell]]. In [[22 ABY/Legends|22 ABY]] while [[Siolu Sporipri]] was its [[Mayor/Legends|mayor]], Lagabee was mostly destroyed by [[Stone mite/Legends|stone mites]].

